=Description=

"We discuss social bookmarking; tagging; the difference between del.icio.us and Ma.gnolia; groups at Ma.gnolia; surprising web sites and blogs they’ve come across using Ma.gnolia; YouTube; linguistics and information architecture; interior desecrations; Jason Santa Maria and Greg Storey; Jeffrey Zeldman; Ma.gnolia’s business model and where they’d like to be a year from now; import bookmarks from del.icio.us and browsers; Web 2.0 they enjoy using; RSS; NetNewsWire; Flickr; Nicholas Negroponte’s Being Digital; Ruby on Rails; Friendster, MySpace and Facebook."

